60int fdt_setprop_inplace_namelen_partial(void *fdt, int nodeoffset,
61 const char *name, int namelen,
62 uint32_t idx, const void *val,
63 int len)
64{
65 void *propval;
66 int proplen;
67
68 propval = fdt_getprop_namelen_w(fdt, nodeoffset, name, namelen,
69 &proplen);
70 if (!propval)
71 return proplen;
72
73 if (proplen < (len + idx))
74 return -FDT_ERR_NOSPACE;
75
76 memcpy((char *)propval + idx, val, len);
77 return 0;
78}
79
80int fdt_setprop_inplace(void *fdt, int nodeoffset, const char *name,
81 const void *val, int len)
82{
83 const void *propval;
84 int proplen;
85
86 propval = fdt_getprop(fdt, nodeoffset, name, &proplen);
87 if (! propval)
88 return proplen;
89
90 if (proplen != len)
91 return -FDT_ERR_NOSPACE;
92
93 return fdt_setprop_inplace_namelen_partial(fdt, nodeoffset, name,
94 strlen(name), 0,
95 val, len);
96}
97
98static void _fdt_nop_region(void *start, int len)
99{
100 fdt32_t *p;
101
102 for (p = start; (char *)p < ((char *)start + len); p++)
103 *p = cpu_to_fdt32(FDT_NOP);
104}
105
106int fdt_nop_property(void *fdt, int nodeoffset, const char *name)
107{
108 struct fdt_property *prop;
109 int len;
110
111 prop = fdt_get_property_w(fdt, nodeoffset, name, &len);
112 if (! prop)
113 return len;
114
115 _fdt_nop_region(prop, len + sizeof(*prop));
116
117 return 0;
118}
119
120int _fdt_node_end_offset(void *fdt, int offset)
121{
122 int depth = 0;
123
124 while ((offset >= 0) && (depth >= 0))
125 offset = fdt_next_node(fdt, offset, &depth);
126
127 return offset;
128}
129
130int fdt_nop_node(void *fdt, int nodeoffset)
131{
132 int endoffset;
133
134 endoffset = _fdt_node_end_offset(fdt, nodeoffset);
135 if (endoffset < 0)
136 return endoffset;
137
138 _fdt_nop_region(fdt_offset_ptr_w(fdt, nodeoffset, 0),
139 endoffset - nodeoffset);
140 return 0;
141}
